  <title>Set custom fonts</title>

<p>There are two ways to change how text looks on your <app>Terminal</app>. 1. Select the option use system fonts 2. set your own font by unchecking the above option and choosing font and size from the font dialog. </p>

<p>The checkbox option 'allow bold text' use bold text to display your <app>Terminal</app> text output. </p> <guiseq><gui style="menu">Edit</gui><gui style="menuitem">Profile Preferences</gui><gui style="tab">Background</gui></guiseq> or press <keyseq><key>Alt</key><key>E</key><key>P</key></keyseq> 
